<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->
<div class="alert alert-info">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl) -->
<a name="eztoc308389_0_1" id="eztoc308389_0_1"></a><h3>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl) -->

<a name="Fordampning" id="Fordampning"></a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl) -->
Fordampningsmålere</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</h3>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>En fordampningsmåler er en varmefordelingsmåler, som virker efter det måleprincip, at væskers fordampningshastighed er afhængig af temperaturen. Måleren er udstyret med et lille glasrør, som sidder foran en skala med tal. Glasrøret er fyldt op med en væske, hvis fordampningshastighed er afhængig af temperaturen på radiatoroverfladen. Jo højere temperaturen er på radiatoroverfladen, jo hurtigere fordamper væsken. Fordampningen fra glasrøret bliver på den måde et udtryk for, hvor meget varme radiatoren afgiver.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Måleren aflæses ved at registrere det antal målestreger, som væsken er sunket. Da fordampningen vil foregå langsommere, efterhånden som væsken synker i røret, er stregafstanden på skalaen større for oven end for neden. Fra start vil glasrøret desuden ofte være fyldt over nulstregen for i nogen grad at kompensere for den fordampning der vil ske, også selvom radiatoren ikke er i brug.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->
<div class="alert alert-info">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl) -->
<a name="eztoc308389_0_2" id="eztoc308389_0_2"></a><h3>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl) -->

<a name="Elektroniske" id="Elektroniske"></a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl) -->
Elektroniske målere</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</h3>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>En elektronisk varmefordelingsmåler virker efter det måleprincip, at temperaturen på overfladen af radiatoren afspejler, hvor meget varme radiatoren afgiver. Temperaturen på overfladen måles med en temperaturføler. Nogle målere er forsynet med to følere, hvor den ene registrerer radiatorens overfladetemperatur, mens den anden registrerer lufttemperaturen i rummet. Måleren registrerer et forbrug, når temperaturen på radiatoroverfladen bliver højere end rumtemperaturen.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Andre elektroniske målere er kun forsynet med en temperaturføler placeret på radiatorens overflade. Her registreres et forbrug, når temperaturen på radiatorens overflade overstiger en på forhånd fastlagt rumtemperatur.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->
<div class="alert alert-info">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl) -->
<a name="eztoc308389_0_3" id="eztoc308389_0_3"></a><h3>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl) -->

<a name="Fordelings" id="Fordelings"></a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl) -->
Fordelingsmåling</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</h3>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Det totale varmeforbrug i en ejendom måles med en varmeenergimåler. Ved fordelingsmåling fordeles det totale varmeforbrug i en ejendom mellem de enkelte boligenheder ved hjælp af varmefordelingsmålere. Korrekt afregning af varmeforbrug på grundlag af varmefordelingsmålere er betinget af, at alle målerne giver samme måleresultat ved en given varmeafgivelse.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>For at de kan gøre det, skal målerne monteres rigtigt i forhold til radiatortype og radiatorens størrelse. Desuden skal tællingen ganges med en såkaldt skalafaktor, der tager højde for radiatorens størrelse og varmeovergangstallet mellem radiatoroverfladen og måleren. På den måde omregnes den tælling, der aflæses på måleren til et udtryk for radiatorens varmeafgivelse og dermed det varmeforbrug, der har været på den pågældende radiator.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Ved udarbejdelse af forbrugsregnskaber fordeles ejendommens varmeforbrug forholdsmæssigt på grundlag af tællingerne på varmefordelingsmålerne.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->
<div class="alert alert-info">
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl) -->
<a name="eztoc308389_0_4" id="eztoc308389_0_4"></a><h3>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl) -->

<a name="Eksempel" id="Eksempel"></a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/anchor.tpl) -->
Eksempel på beregning af en boligenheds varmeforbrug med varmefordelingsmålere:</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</h3>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/header.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Totalt varmeforbrug i ejendommen (aflæst på varmeenergimåler):</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>200.000 kilowattimer til en samlet pris af 180.000 kr.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Hvis 50 % af varmeforbruget i ejendommen fordeles ved hjælp af varmefordelingsmålere afregnes der for 90.000 kr.</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

Summen af samtlige tællinger aflæst på varmefordelingsmålere i ejendommen er 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>500</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
 streger.<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->
Antallet af streger kan være korrigeret for udsat beliggenhed og de 500 streger er da summen af de korrigerede enheder.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Prisen pr streg bliver da kr. 90.000/500 = 180 kr. pr. streg</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Summen af tællinger aflæst på varmefordelingsmålere i boligenheden er 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>30</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
 streger.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Andelen af boligenhedens energiforbrug bliver da&nbsp;30 Streger a kr. 180, = 5.400 kr.</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>De 50 % af varmeudgifterne som ikke er fordelt ved hjælp af varmefordelingsmålere omfatter typisk fast afgift til fjernvarmeværket, bidrag til det varme vand, varmetabet fra cirkulation og varmtvandsbeholder, opvarmning af fællesarealer og varmetab fra rør i varmeanlægge</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
</div>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/InfoBox.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
      
      
